FBIS3-39782 "drweu035_q_94008" FBIS-WEU-94-035 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Feb 1994 TURKEY Armenia Seeks Turkish Mediation NC2102175694 London Kanal-6 Television in Turkish 1700 GMT 21 Feb 94 NC2102175694 London Kanal-6 Television Language: Turkish Article Type:BFN [Text] Armenia is asking for Turkey's help in making peace with Azerbaijan. Zhirair Liparityan, deputy foreign minister of Armenia, arrived in Ankara last night and met Foreign Minister Hikmet Cetin this morning. The meeting was held at Armenia's request. Armenia, which has become a supplicant for peace because of the latest Azerbaijani military successes and worsening economic conditions, expects Turkey to contribute to peace in Caucasus.
